10 §1431. Definitions
11 As used in this Chapter, the following words have the meaning ascribed to
12 them in this Section unless the context clearly indicates otherwise:
13 * * *
14 (35) "Residential real property" means real property consisting of one or not
15 more than four residential dwelling units, which are buildings or structures each of
